f(B) = \sum_{k=1}^6 (y_k-Bx_k)^2
\frac{df(B)}{dB} = -2 \sum_{k=1}^6 x_k(y_k-Bx_k) = -2 ((\sum_{k=1}^6 x_ky_k)-B (\sum_{k=1}^6 x_k^2))
\frac{df(B)}{dB} =0
\frac{df(B)}{dB} = -2 ((\sum_{k=1}^6 x_ky_k)-B (\sum_{k=1}^6 x_k^2)) = 0
B
B = \frac{\sum_{k=1}^6 x_ky_k}{\sum_{k=1}^6 x_k^2}
